        {
            "_id": "0jmGWs55RI53ul3s",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Desiccated Boulder Breath",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The draconic fumecrux belches forth a mass of stones that are partially solid and partially void energy. These stones deal @Damage[4d8[bludgeoning],4d8[void]|options:area-damage] damage in a @Template[type:cone|distance:30] (@Check[reflex|dc:25|basic] save).</p>\n<p>It can't use Desiccated Boulder Breath again for [[/br 1d4 #Recharge Desiccated Boulder Breath]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
